vector — ACS-002 §5.2 (shortest-form applies to length prefixes, matching the existing
`non-shortest-len` vector) and ACS-004 §6.3 (integer range-coverage note: int=i64, u32; the
[2^63,2^64-1] band has no v1 type code) — plus one new instance negative vector
`instance-int-above-i64` (36 rows total). NOT ratified by CCP-007 and still open: #20 (ACS-004
urn↔type binding — an ambiguous "modulo namespace" design decision) and #21 (ACS-005 GL-015
